    skos:definition "Human gene entity (Entrez/NCBI model). Separate from protein product to properly distinguish genotype from phenotype. Key ALS genes: C9orf72, SOD1, TARDBP, FUS, TBK1, NEK1, SQSTM1, VCP, OPTN." ;
    skos:exactMatch biolink:Gene ;
    skos:inScheme <https://cair2015.github.io/als-kg> .

